1
00:00:04,450 --> 00:00:07,044
你愿意的话可以坐下
Sit down if you want to.

2
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,384
我不知我会遇到谁
I didn't know who I might meet

3
00:00:09,457 --> 00:00:10,890
或他们会问我什么
or what they might ask.

4
00:00:10,958 --> 00:00:13,722
你有没有乘过真正的捕虾船？
You ever been on a real shrimp boat?

5
00:00:13,795 --> 00:00:15,558
没有
No.

6
00:00:15,630 --> 00:00:18,394
可我乘过一条真正的大捕虾船
But I been on a real big boat.

7
00:00:18,468 --> 00:00:21,403
我指的是一种专门捕虾的船
I'm talking about a shrimp catching boat.

8
00:00:21,471 --> 00:00:24,406
我一直都在捕虾船上干活
I been working on shrimp boats all my life .

9
00:00:24,475 --> 00:00:26,739
开始是我叔叔的船
I started out on my uncle's boat

10
00:00:26,811 --> 00:00:28,745
那时我大概9岁
when I was about maybe 9.

11
00:00:28,813 --> 00:00:31,748
我刚在考虑自己去买一条船
I was just looking into buying my own boat

12
00:00:31,817 --> 00:00:33,751
然后就应征入伍了
and got drafted.

13
00:00:33,819 --> 00:00:37,084
我的名字叫本杰明巴弗布鲁
My given name is Benjamin Buford Blue.

14
00:00:37,157 --> 00:00:39,421
人们都管我叫布巴
People call me Bubba,

15
00:00:39,494 --> 00:00:41,928
好像个乡下佬的名字
just like one of them old red neck boys.

16
00:00:41,996 --> 00:00:43,258
很难以置信吧？
Can you believe that?

17
00:00:43,332 --> 00:00:45,425
我叫福雷斯甘
My name's Forrest Gump.

18
00:00:45,501 --> 00:00:47,765
人们都管我叫福雷斯甘
People call me Forrest Gump.

19
00:00:47,837 --> 00:00:50,772
布巴来自亚拉巴州拉巴特湾
So Bubba was from Bayou La Batre, Alabama,

20
00:00:50,841 --> 00:00:52,570
他的妈妈是煮虾的
and his mama cooked shrimp.

21
00:00:54,545 --> 00:00:56,911
她的妈妈也是煮虾的
And her mama before her cooked shrimp,

22
00:00:56,982 --> 00:01:00,577
还有她妈妈的妈妈也是煮虾的
and her mama before her mama cooked shrimp, too.

23
00:01:00,653 --> 00:01:02,416
布巴家的人了解所有
Bubba's family knew everything

24
00:01:02,488 --> 00:01:04,922
跟捕虾有关的事情
there was to know about the shrimping business.

25
00:01:04,992 --> 00:01:07,256
我知道所有
I know everything there is to know

26
00:01:07,327 --> 00:01:08,589
跟捕虾有关的事情
about the shrimping business.

27
00:01:08,663 --> 00:01:11,097
我自己也准备去捕虾
I'm going into the shrimping business for myself

28
00:01:11,166 --> 00:01:13,430
等我退伍之后
after I get out of the army.

